---
title: Veggie Couscous Bowl with Creamy Feta Sauce & Garlic Pita Chips
description: We’re big fans of the ubiquitous “power bowl,” but we have to admit: this one’s extra special. It’s a one-bowl feast that’s positively bursting with flavor. The base is a heap of fluffy couscous simmered with stock, scallions, and lemon zest. On top, there’s roasted, warm-spiced zucchini, bell pepper, and shallot drizzled in a creamy feta sauce. On the side, you’ve got crunchy, garlicky pita chips for dipping. One bite will have you totally bowled over.
